<section id="accessibility-{{ section.id }}" class="accessibility-section">
  <div class="accessibility-container">
    <h2 class="accessibility-title">Accessibility Statement</h2>
    
    <div class="accessibility-content">
      <div class="accessibility-intro">
        <p>New Thrifts is committed to ensuring digital accessibility for all users, including those with disabilities. We are continuously improving the user experience for everyone and applying the relevant accessibility standards.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="accessibility-standards">
        <h3>Conformance Status</h3>
        <p>We aim to conform to the Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG) 2.1, Level A and AA standards. This website is partially conformant with WCAG 2.1 Level AA.</p>
        
        <div class="compliance-badges">
          <div class="badge-item">
            <span class="badge-icon">‚ôø</span>
            <span class="badge-text">WCAG 2.1 AA</span>
          </div>
          <div class="badge-item">
            <span class="badge-icon">‚å®Ô∏è</span>
            <span class="badge-text">Keyboard Navigation</span>
          </div>
          <div class="badge-item">
            <span class="badge-icon">üîç</span>
            <span class="badge-text">Screen Reader Compatible</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="accessibility-features">
        <h3>Accessibility Features</h3>
        <div class="features-grid">
          <div class="feature-item">
            <h4>Keyboard Navigation</h4>
            <p>All interactive elements can be accessed using keyboard navigation. Use Tab to move forward, Shift+Tab to move backward, and Enter or Space to activate.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="feature-item">
            <h4>Screen Reader Support</h4>
            <p>Our website is optimized for screen readers with proper heading structure, alt text for images, and ARIA labels where needed.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="feature-item">
            <h4>Color Contrast</h4>
            <p>We maintain sufficient color contrast ratios (4.5:1 for normal text, 3:1 for large text) to ensure readability.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="feature-item">
            <h4>Text Scaling</h4>
            <p>Text can be scaled up to 200% without loss of functionality or content. Use your browser's zoom feature or text scaling options.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="feature-item">
            <h4>Focus Indicators</h4>
            <p>Clear focus indicators are provided for all interactive elements to help users navigate with keyboard or assistive technologies.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="feature-item">
            <h4>Alternative Text</h4>
            <p>All images include descriptive alternative text to provide context for users who cannot see the images.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="accessibility-tools">
        <h3>Accessibility Tools</h3>
        <div class="tools-section">
          <div class="tool-item">
            <button class="tool-btn" onclick="toggleHighContrast()" aria-label="Toggle high contrast mode">
              <span class="tool-icon">üåì</span>
              <span>High Contrast</span>
            </button>
          </div>
          
          <div class="tool-item">
            <button class="tool-btn" onclick="toggleLargeText()" aria-label="Toggle large text mode">
              <span class="tool-icon">üîç</span>
              <span>Large Text</span>
            </button>
          </div>
          
          <div class="tool-item">
            <button class="tool-btn" onclick="toggleReducedMotion()" aria-label="Toggle reduced motion">
              <span class="tool-icon">üé¨</span>
              <span>Reduce Motion</span>
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="accessibility-feedback">
        <h3>Feedback & Contact</h3>
        <p>We welcome your feedback on the accessibility of New Thrifts. Please let us know if you encounter accessibility barriers:</p>
        
        <div class="contact-methods">
          <div class="contact-item">
            <strong>Email:</strong> accessibility@newthrifts.com
          </div>
          <div class="contact-item">
            <strong>Phone:</strong> 1-800-NEW-THRIFTS (1-800-639-8474)
          </div>
          <div class="contact-item">
            <strong>Response Time:</strong> We typically respond within 2 business days.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="accessibility-updates">
        <h3>Recent Updates</h3>
        <ul class="updates-list">
          <li>Added keyboard navigation support for all interactive elements</li>
          <li>Improved color contrast ratios throughout the site</li>
          <li>Enhanced screen reader compatibility</li>
          <li>Added focus indicators for better navigation</li>
          <li>Implemented ARIA labels for dynamic content</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

